      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm a bit confused. If you look at the actual content of their answers, they are basically saying the exact same thing. Both said they listened, empathized, and worked to find a solution. Why do you think Candidate B lacks clarity or struggles to articulate solutions when the substance of their answer is identical to Candidate A's? Is it just the way they talk?",
